data.description:
Need assistance with closing costs or making your interest rate lower? These sellers are offering up to a 1.5% contribution to assist with those things. 

This 4 bed, 2.5 bath home is perfect for your family's comfort. The master suite is your personal retreat on the main floor, while the kids' rooms are cozily nestled upstairs. Practicality meets style with walk-in closets in 3 bedrooms and 2 sinks in the master bathroom. The huge loft provides versatility - a living space, homeschool room, toy room, or exercise room. The backyard is very nicely landscaped with turf, pergola, play set, and trampoline. Plus there is an electric car charger in the garage!

The house is conveniently located nearby two great neighborhood parks and is in walking distance to Cactus Trails Elementary. Make this home yours today!
